bibliothek.gui.dock.toolbar.expand

Class DisabledExpandableToolbarItemStrategy

  • java.lang.Object
    • bibliothek.gui.dock.toolbar.expand.DisabledExpandableToolbarItemStrategy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExpandableToolbarItemStrategy

    public class DisabledExpandableToolbarItemStrategy
extends Object
implements ExpandableToolbarItemStrategy
    This implementation of ExpandableToolbarItemStrategy does not do anything, it just disables any feature related to expandable items.
    Author:
    Benjamin Sigg
